      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FASCINATE ABBY (2) showed good early burn but run over late to finish 7th at this track in Grade 4/5 company. Tough to beat if on-song. TEAPOT SCANDAL (1) finished third (23.28) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 7th at Taree Super Track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and nine minor placings to her credit. Key runner on best form. AUSSIE BELL (4) has mixed form a little and missed the frame the last two but was a Grade 5 winner three back (23.42) at this track over 400m. Can hit the frame this time. ALCARAZ (3) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
